Appifyer
==========

Appifyer is an application launcher.

Add your own apps or get some from http://www.appifyer.com, and set them up to launch automatically, via the Appifyer menu, or by using a hotkey.

Appifyer is intended to make it as easy as possible to launch small on-demand applications as well as other applications that you use daily.

Note: User settings and image resources are saved in %AppData%\Appifyer.

Default hotkeys
--------------------
* Windows+Space brings forth the app menu
* Middleclick the start button (or leftclick the tray icon) to bring forth the app menu